2. The 22nd day of December 2022 is appointed as the day on which the 
following provisions of the Air Navigation and Transport Act 2022 (No. 40 of 
2022) shall come into operation: 

(a) Part 1 (other than section 8); 

(b) Part 2; 

(c) Part 8; 

(d) Part 9; 

(e) Part 10 (other than section 97); 

(f) Part 11. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

21 December, 2022. 

EAMON RYAN, 
Minister for Transport. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 13th January, 2023. 



















